  "industry_note": "ASTM A516 Grade 70 / SA-516-70 / EN P355GH (~) — pressure vessel plate carbon steel for moderate / lower temp service (-29°C). C ≤ 0.27, Mn 0.79-1.30, Si 0.13-0.45 (HIC service grade). σy 260 / UTS 485-620 / El 21% / Charpy V-notch min @ -29°C = 27J. Normalized 권장 (>50 mm 두께). 화학 plant pressure vessel, boiler drum, heat exchanger shell, LPG storage. 한국 KS B0801 KP70 동등.",
